Package: bccamtrap
Title: Tools for QA and validation of Camera Trap data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Andy", "Teucher", , "andy.teucher@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7840-692X")),
    person("Province of British Columbia", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Allows the easy and semi-automated checking, validation, and exploration
    of camera trap data collected according to BC RISC standards, and tagged using 
    TimeLapse software.
